### Variables
@id = your-task-id-here

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks

### Get All Tasks (Filtered & Sorted)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?status=todo&priority=high&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc

### Create Task
# @name createTask
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Build REST API",
  "description": "Implement CRUD for tasks using Express and TypeScript",
  "status": "in-progress",
  "priority": "high",
  "tags": ["express", "typescript", "rest"]
}

### Get Task By ID (Use ID from Create Task response)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/{{createTask.response.body.id}}

### Update Task
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/{{createTask.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
}

### Delete Task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/{{createTask.response.body.id}}

### Metrics
GET http://localhost:3000/metrics

### OpenAPI Docs
GET http://localhost:3000/docs
